name: Sazerac
prepTime: 2 minutes
cookTime: 0 minutes
portions: 1

ingredients:
  - (3/2 oz)   Rye Whisky
  - (1/4 oz)   Absinth
  - (1 tsp)    Sugar
  - (3 dashes) Peychaud's Bitters
  - (1 twist)  Lemon Rind

steps:
  - Coat the inside of a chilled rocks glass with Absinth
  - Stir remaining ingredients seperately in shaker with ice
  - Pour remaining absinth out of the glass and strain mixture into glass
  - Add lemon twist for garnish
